response.overview: Gorgeous fortune teller Selina (Jewelz Blu) and her spirited assistant Leah (Kimmy Kimm) spend their days arranging palm readings for a colorful cast of clients, but when it comes to love, they're as unlucky as anyone. After Selina reads the palm of the mysterious Anastasia (Vanessa Sky) and uncovers a steamy affair, she and Leah are swept into a wild, sexy adventure across Hollywood. Guided by visions of passion, friendship, and chaos, including run-ins with jealous ex-girlfriends, Selina must navigate a future she never saw coming. Will she finally find the love she's been searching for?
response.title: Visions
